metadata.name: Up close and personal
metadata.description: over a period of two years and numerous visits i tracked a family of wild boar in the forest of dean one of the few remaining acient woodlands in the uk covering more than 42 sq miles, i managed to capture some unique images of these elusive and secretive creatures, to get this image i was laid under camo netting using a wild angle lens whilst the large wild boar foraged the forest floor right in front of me.
